Communities.community_description: Supports financial operations, planning, internal control and regulatory requirements.

Covers data related to financial planning, performance analysis, and management reporting. Supports budget, forecast, and strategic planning cycles. Ensures consistent, high-quality financial data across the Group and serves as the single source of truth for key functions (e. g., HR, CSR, IR).

Covers accounting data across the Group, ensuring consistency in financial reporting, compliance and audit readiness. Manages consolidation processes, accounting policies, impairment testing and interactions with auditors and regulators.

Covers tax-related data including policy, compliance, and risk management. Designs tax data structures, monitors reforms, and ensure alignment with the Group's strategy and legal requirements. Supports tax audits, defense, and CSR integration.

Covers data related to risk management and insurance policies, including risk identification, mitigation, and insurance programs. Ensures reliable, centralized data to support informed risk decisions, claims handling, and compliance across the Group

Covers data for treasury operations, cash flow and financing. Covers policy implementation, cash optimization, guarantees, and internal financing. Supports short- and long-term liquidity planning with accurate, timely data and decision-making.

Covers data management for acquisitions, disposals and partnerships. Coordinate transaction data from deal origination to execution, ensuring compliance with Group standards. Supports portfolio strategy with accurate data on synergies, growth, and value creation.

Steer the climate objectives of the group, through GHG emissions measurement and projections, with attenuations and adaptations plans. Allows the right climate internal and external reporting. Contains all factors to calculate precise emissions linked to all the activities of the group.
Steer the nature objectives of the group through measurable impacts of the group's activities. Objects such as biodiversity, pollution, ressources consumption & circular economy, water.
